Published on May 9, 2016 10:38 am
Madhuri Dixit, her husband Dr Sriram Nene watched the Beauty and the Beast musical with their sons Arin and Raayan on Sunday (May 8).
It is very rare that Dhak Dhak actress' sons are spotted in public.
The boys were seen in striped t shirts and jeans as they walked with their parents.
(Source: Photo by Varinder Chawla)
Shilpa Shetty was also spotted with her husband Raj Kundra and son Viaan Raj Kundra.
(Source: Photo by Varinder Chawla)
Former cricketer Rahul Dravid was also seen with his son.
(Source: Photo by Varinder Chawla)
Madhuri, Raayan, Arin and Dr Nene with a guest.
(Source: Photo by Varinder Chawla)
Shilpa Shetty was chic in a white shirt worn with a pleated skirt and flats.
Her son was in white and jeans.
(Source: Photo by Varinder Chawla)
Singer Shaan and wife with their sons.
(Source: Photo by Varinder Chawla)
Shilpa's parents also attended the musical with their younger daughter Shamita Shetty.
(Source: Photo by Varinder Chawla)
Actress Sarah Jane Dais was cheery in a short yellow dress.
(Source: Photo by Varinder Chawla)
CEO of Disney India Sidharth Roy Kapur was also at the screening.
(Source: Photo by Varinder Chawla)
